author: Squidmar Miniatures
description:
Sign up to Milanote for free with no time-limit: https://milanote.com/squidmar

This week, we put an amateur and an intermediate painter up against one of the worlds best Warhammer Miniature Painters; Neil Hollis. With 14 golden 
demons and 2 Slayer Swords he needs a challenge. With a budget of $10 for the professional and $1000 for the amateur, can we level the playing field?
